title: Moab 2016 Trail Cat Jeep
description:
Ever wanted to see a Jeep Wrangler stuffed with a 6.2 liter supercharged V8, mated to a 6-speed manual transmission? The Jeep TrailCat does just that.

Revealed at the 2016 Easter Jeep Safari in Moab, Utah.
